  <summary date="2019-11-15T18:48:24Z" status="Introduced in House">Aviation Incentive Pay Parity Act

This bill revises the authority for payment of aviation incentive pay to reserve component officers. It permits the amount of such pay to be equal to that of an officer in the regular component of the particular uniformed service.</summary>
